  <entry>
    <title>二叉树的三种深度优先遍历</title>
    <url>/2021/02/18/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本文主要对二叉树深度优先算法的实现进行梳理，并给出相应的代码。深度优先各种遍历顺序的递归实现都很简单，此处只关注非递归实现。这其中最为关键的是中序遍历和后序遍历。宽度优先写过很多次了，比较简单。</p>
<h3 id="前序遍历"><a href="#前序遍历" class="headerlink" title="前序遍历"></a>前序遍历</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">preorderTraversal</span><span class="params">(TreeNode *root, <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; &amp;res)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">stack</span>&lt;TreeNode*&gt; stk;</span><br><span class="line">    stk.push(root);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!stk.empty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *cur = stk.top();</span><br><span class="line">        stk.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        res.push_back(cur-&gt;val);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;right) stk.push(cur-&gt;right);   <span class="comment">// NOTE：先入右边，再入左边 </span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;left) stk.push(cur-&gt;left);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="后序遍历"><a href="#后序遍历" class="headerlink" title="后序遍历"></a>后序遍历</h3><p>后序遍历稍微麻烦一些，我出于兴趣，在此总结了三种实现方式。</p>
<p>第一种直接利用先序遍历（不同于上面的先序）的结果。后序遍历的顺序为左、右、中，可按中、右、左的顺序遍历二叉树（这仅为另一种先序遍历而已），然后将遍历结果的序列反转。这种方式并不像很多人说的那样不堪，下面将要列举的另外两种实现方式，只是将这里用于反转vector的时间分摊在了循环的迭代过程中而已。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">postorderTraversal</span><span class="params">(TreeNode *root, <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; &amp;res)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">stack</span>&lt;TreeNode*&gt; stk;</span><br><span class="line">    stk.push(root);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!stk.empty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *cur = stk.top();</span><br><span class="line">        stk.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        res.push_back(cur-&gt;val);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;left) stk.push(cur-&gt;left);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;right) stk.push(cur-&gt;right);   <span class="comment">// 仅修改这里的顺序为先入左，再入右 </span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    reverse(res.begin(), res.end());</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>接下来的两种实现方式同样按中、右、左的顺序对节点执行入栈操作。每次迭代时，先判断栈顶结点是否有子结点，如果没有，直接弹栈。如果有子结点，则判断子结点是否被访问过，如果子结点也被访问过了，亦弹栈。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">postorderTraversal</span><span class="params">(TreeNode *root, <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; &amp;res)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">stack</span>&lt;TreeNode*&gt; stk;</span><br><span class="line">    stk.push(root);</span><br><span class="line">    TreeNode *visited = <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!stk.empty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *cur = stk.top();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ((!cur-&gt;left &amp;&amp; !cur-&gt;right) || (visited &amp;&amp; (visited == cur-&gt;left || visited == cur-&gt;right))) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            stk.pop();</span><br><span class="line">            res.push_back(cur-&gt;val);</span><br><span class="line">            visited = cur;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;right) stk.push(cur-&gt;right);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;left) stk.push(cur-&gt;left);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>最后一种实现方式是从leetcode上一位朋友的<a class="link"   href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/binary-tree-postorder-traversal/solution/a-li-mian-shi-ti-zhi-yong-zhan-qu-zuo-er-cha-shu-d/" >题解<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>中看到的，该方式运用了一个小技巧。在每次迭代时，如果是第一次遍历到某个结点，就马上压入一个空元素。这使得在第二次遍历该结点前，必定会先遍历到一个空元素，即该空元素成为了第二次遍历的信号。于是，当栈顶元素为空元素时，可一次性弹出两个元素。这种方式使得代码的逻辑变得简单了许多。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">postorderTraversal</span><span class="params">(TreeNode *root, <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; &amp;res)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">stack</span>&lt;TreeNode*&gt; stk;</span><br><span class="line">    stk.push(root);</span><br><span class="line">    TreeNode *visited = <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!stk.empty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *cur = stk.top();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!cur) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            stk.pop();</span><br><span class="line">            visited = stk.top();</span><br><span class="line">            res.push_back(visited-&gt;val);</span><br><span class="line">            stk.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            stk.push(<span class="literal">nullptr</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;right) stk.push(cur-&gt;right);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;left) stk.push(cur-&gt;left);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="中序遍历"><a href="#中序遍历" class="headerlink" title="中序遍历"></a>中序遍历</h3><p>中序遍历较之后序遍历要难一些，因为思路并不是很直观，但代码很简洁，值得背下来。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">postorderTraversal</span><span class="params">(TreeNode *root, <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; &amp;res)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">stack</span>&lt;TreeNode*&gt; stk;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (root || !stk.empty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (root) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            stk.push(root);</span><br><span class="line">            root = root-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *cur = stk.top();</span><br><span class="line">        stk.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        res.push_back(cur-&gt;val);</span><br><span class="line">        root = cur-&gt;right;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>算法</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>二叉树</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>在二叉搜索树中查找后继及删除结点</title>
    <url>/2021/02/07/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A0%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E7%BB%93%E7%82%B9/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>二叉搜索树（后称BST）的性质比较简单，本文关注各结点关键字互不相同的BST中后继结点的查找以及结点的删除操作。</p>
<h3 id="查找后继"><a href="#查找后继" class="headerlink" title="查找后继"></a>查找后继</h3><p>一个结点x的后继是大于x.key的最小关键字的结点，即在BST中序遍历中x的后一个结点，类似地，可以定义x的前驱。对于一个结点x，如果存在它的后继y，分两种情况：若x存在右子树，则y为其右子树的最左结点；否则，若x的右子树为空，则y为x的最底层祖先，且该祖先的左孩子也是x的祖先。上述结论直接给出了后继的查找算法，算法的实现比较简单（leetcode No.1882）。此处给出对上述结论的证明。</p>
<p>我们先说明当x的右子树为空时的情形。首先，y一定是x的祖先。否则，一定存在y和x的公共祖先z，使得x &lt; z &lt; y，即y与x之间还有其它的结点，这与y是x的后继相矛盾。其次，x一定在y的左子树上，即y的左孩子也是x的祖先（祖先可以是结点本身）。最后，若有z而非y为满足上述条件的最底层祖先，则y是z的祖先，且z位于y的左子树上，导致x &lt; z &lt; y，矛盾。接着，我们来说明当x的右子树非空时的情形。若后继不在x的右子树上，则采用与前述在x的右子树为空这一情形下相同的分析可以得到相同的后继y。但显然，x的右子树上的任意结点z都满足x &lt; z &lt; y，这与y为x的后继相矛盾。因此，y必定在x的右子树上，从而y为x的右子树的最左结点。</p>
<p>具体的代码实现如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">TreeNode* <span class="title">inorderSuccessor</span><span class="params">(TreeNode* root, TreeNode* p)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root || !p) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    TreeNode *successor = <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (p-&gt;right) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        successor = p-&gt;right;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (successor-&gt;left)</span><br><span class="line">            successor = successor-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *cur = root;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (cur != p) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (p-&gt;val &lt; cur-&gt;val) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                successor = cur;</span><br><span class="line">                cur = cur-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                cur = cur-&gt;right; </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> successor;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="删除节点"><a href="#删除节点" class="headerlink" title="删除节点"></a>删除节点</h3><p>设要删除的结点为z，则在BST中删除结点可以简要地分为以下几种情况。若z没有子结点，则直接删除z。若z只有一个子结点，则将以该子结点为根的子树提到z的位置上。若z有两个子结点，则可以将z的后继结点移到z的位置上。当然，在具体情形下还需要考虑一些小问题，比如z的父节点存在时要修改z的父节点，将z的后继移到z的位置时要分后继是否为z的子结点。以leetcode No.450为例，该题给出一棵树以及要删除的结点。下面的代码采用递归，比较优雅地实现了结点的删除，在代码注释中给出了对细节的处理。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">TreeNode* <span class="title">deleteNode</span><span class="params">(TreeNode *root, <span class="keyword">int</span> key)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (key &lt; root-&gt;val) &#123; root-&gt;left = deleteNode(root-&gt;left, key); <span class="keyword">return</span> root; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (key &gt; root-&gt;val) &#123; root-&gt;right = deleteNode(root-&gt;right, key); <span class="keyword">return</span> root; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/* 根结点为要删除的结点*/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!root-&gt;left || !root-&gt;right) &#123;      <span class="comment">// 包含了除存在两个子结点之外的其它情况</span></span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode * tmp = !root-&gt;left ? root-&gt;right : root-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">delete</span>(root);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> tmp;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TreeNode *successor = root-&gt;right;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!successor-&gt;left) &#123;             <span class="comment">// 若后继为root的子结点</span></span><br><span class="line">            successor-&gt;left = root-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            TreeNode sentinel(<span class="number">0</span>, successor, <span class="literal">nullptr</span>), *pa = &amp;sentinel;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> (successor-&gt;left) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                successor = successor-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">                pa = pa-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            pa-&gt;left = successor-&gt;right;    <span class="comment">// <span class="doctag">NOTE:</span> 若后继有右孩子，需要把右子树提到了后继的位置上</span></span><br><span class="line">            successor-&gt;left = root-&gt;left;</span><br><span class="line">            successor-&gt;right = root-&gt;right;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">delete</span>(root);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> successor;        </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>算法</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>二叉搜索树</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>生产者-消费者模型及其实现</title>
    <url>/2021/02/21/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%80%85-%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E8%80%85%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>线程提供的强大的信息共享能力是有代价的。多线程程序必须使用互斥量和条件变量等同步工具来协调对共享变量的访问。本文在Linux系统下实现生产者-消费者模型。</p>
<p>仅使用互斥量，可以实现一个简单版本的生产者-消费者模型，该版本中生产者和消费者的关键代码如下。在该情形下，生产者通过忙等的方式不断询问是否有产品可以使用。这其中的问题在于，当消费者发现没有产品时，它会不断地执行获取锁、检查变量状态、释放锁的操作，直到它因为时间片耗尽而被切换。忙等的时候浪费了大量的CPU资源。因此，更好的方式是让消费者在没有产品时进入休眠状态，当有产品了便及时地唤醒它。这时候条件变量就派上用场了。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 生产者</span></span><br><span class="line">assert(pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mtx) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">buffer++;</span><br><span class="line">assert(pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mtx) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 消费者</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (;;) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mtx) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (buffer &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        buffer--;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mtx) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>使用条件变量进行同步的一对相互协作的操作是pthread_cond_signal和pthread_cond_wait，或者pthread_cond_broadcast和pthread_cond_wait。broadcast方式会唤醒所有阻塞在条件变量上的线程，而signal只会唤醒一个线程。虽然总是使用broadcast并不会出现什么大问题，但是它更适用于被阻塞线程执行的任务各不相同的情况。如果多个执行相同任务的线程（比如消费者）阻塞在同一个条件变量上，使用pthread_cond_signal的效率会更高。具体的实现如下。在该具体情形下，有三个生产者和一个消费者，每个生产者需要各自生产5个产品。消费者消耗15个产品之后线程终止。值得一提的是，虽然生产者中pthread_cond_signal和pthread_mutex_unlock的顺序并无强制规定，但在先释放锁、后通知时，消费者在被唤醒之前可能锁已经被其它生产者获取，从而消费者在继续执行pthread_cond_wait时发现锁已经被获取，马上又进入阻塞。因而在输出中显示，消费者单次循环消耗的产品数量经常多于1个。而如果是先通知、后释放锁，则消费者往往会尽快地醒来，并获取锁，于是单次循环消耗的产品数经常为1个。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;pthread.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;assert.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;unistd.h&gt;     // sleep</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> buffer = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">pthread_mutex_t</span> mutex = PTHREAD_MUTEX_INITIALIZER;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">pthread_cond_t</span> cond = PTHREAD_COND_INITIALIZER;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span>*</span><br><span class="line">producer(<span class="keyword">void</span> *arg) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> num_required = <span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; num_required; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sleep(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mutex) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        buffer++;</span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mutex) == <span class="number">0</span>);  <span class="comment">// unlock和signal的顺序并没有强制规定</span></span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_cond_signal(&amp;cond) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span>*</span><br><span class="line">consumer(<span class="keyword">void</span> *arg) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> num_required = <span class="number">15</span>, cnt = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">time_t</span> t = time(<span class="literal">NULL</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (cnt &lt; num_required) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mutex) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (buffer == <span class="number">0</span>)     <span class="comment">// NOTE</span></span><br><span class="line">            assert(pthread_cond_wait(&amp;cond, &amp;mutex) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (buffer &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            buffer--;</span><br><span class="line">            cnt++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;time: %ld, cnt = %d\n&quot;</span>, time(<span class="literal">NULL</span>)-t, cnt);</span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mutex) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pthread_t</span> tid;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">3</span>; ++i) </span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_create(&amp;tid, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, producer, <span class="literal">NULL</span>) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_create(&amp;tid, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, consumer, <span class="literal">NULL</span>) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    pthread_join(tid, <span class="literal">NULL</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>






]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>操作系统</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>多线程</tag>
        <tag>线程同步</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>线程特有数据的两个应用场景</title>
    <url>/2021/02/23/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="协程库中的调度器"><a href="#协程库中的调度器" class="headerlink" title="协程库中的调度器"></a>协程库中的调度器</h3><p>在实现运行在线程模型之上的协程框架时，考虑让一个线程被多个协程所复用，每一个线程要在内部对其上的所有协程进行调度。因此，每一个线程要维护一个自己的调度器。协程在yield到调度器时必须获取调度器的上下文，所以我们要让协程能够访问到自己所属调度器的信息。我们不能简单地定义一个全局的sched变量，因为全局变量会被所有的线程所共享。由于不同的协程执行的函数也不相同，所以我们又需要一定的“全局”特性，使得所有协程都可以访问线程上的sched变量。对此，Linux的线程特有数据提供了解决方案。</p>
<p>线程特有数据可以创建一个全局的key，任何线程都可以对该key关联一份自己的数据。线程通过pthread_setspecific接口来设置自己要关联的数据，pthread_getspecific读取该数据。由于这个key是在协程框架的库函数uthread_create中创建的（用户不可见），用户可以多次调用uthread_create，但该库函数不能多次创建这个key。pthread_once使得只有第一个执行到该处的线程才会真正调用pthread_once指示的函数，pthread_once会使用一个“只执行一次”的标识。关键的代码如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">pthread_key_t</span> uthread_sched_key;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">pthread_once_t</span> key_once = PTHREAD_ONCE_INIT;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span></span><br><span class="line">_uthread_key_create() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_create_key(&amp;uthread_sched_key, <span class="literal">NULL</span>) == <span class="number">0</span>);  <span class="comment">// 创建key，未绑定destructor</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> </span><br><span class="line">uthread_create(struct uthread **new_ut, <span class="keyword">void</span> *func, <span class="keyword">void</span> *arg) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// ...</span></span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_once(&amp;key_once, _uthread_key_create) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">sched</span>* <span class="title">sched</span> =</span> pthread_getspecific(uthread_sched_key);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (sched == <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// create a scheduler...</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// ...</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="库函数中的字符串缓冲区"><a href="#库函数中的字符串缓冲区" class="headerlink" title="库函数中的字符串缓冲区"></a>库函数中的字符串缓冲区</h3><p>《linux/Unix系统编程手册》中介绍了另一个场景。strerror库函数（位于string.h）用于返回指定errno的错误信息，它返回指向文本信息的指针，文本存放在静态分配的内存中。显然这个库函数是不可重入的，我们尝试设计strerror的一个可重入版本。通过线程特有数据，每个调用strerror的线程都会有一份自己的字符串缓冲区（通过malloc动态分配），于是各个线程对strerror的调用互不干扰。动态分配的内存可以通过为key绑定一个destructor，从而在线程终止时释放。值得一提的是，通过valgrind验证内存释放情况得知：若某个线程执行了exit，那么其它线程会马上退出，该情形下与key绑定的destructor不会被执行。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;pthread.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;errno.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;assert.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">pthread_key_t</span> strerror_key;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">pthread_once_t</span> once = PTHREAD_ONCE_INIT;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> MAX_ERRNO_LEN 256</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span></span><br><span class="line">strerror_destructor(<span class="keyword">void</span> *data) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">free</span>(data);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span></span><br><span class="line">strerror_key_create() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_key_create(&amp;strerror_key, strerror_destructor) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> *</span><br><span class="line">strerror(<span class="keyword">int</span> err) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">char</span> *buf;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_once(&amp;once, strerror_key_create) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    buf = pthread_getspecific(strerror_key);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (buf == <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ((buf = <span class="built_in">malloc</span>(MAX_ERRNO_LEN)) == <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            perror(<span class="string">&quot;malloc&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">exit</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        assert(pthread_setspecific(strerror_key, buf) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (err &lt; <span class="number">0</span> || err &gt;= sys_nerr || sys_errlist[err] == <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">snprintf</span>(buf, MAX_ERRNO_LEN, <span class="string">&quot;Unknown error %d&quot;</span>, err);  <span class="comment">// snprintf会在末尾自动添加&#x27;\0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">strncpy</span>(buf, sys_errlist[err], MAX_ERRNO_LEN<span class="number">-1</span>);    </span><br><span class="line">        buf[MAX_ERRNO_LEN] = <span class="string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;  <span class="comment">// 如果指定长度小于被复制字符串的长度，那么不会在末尾添加&#x27;\0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> buf;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> *</span><br><span class="line">thread_func(<span class="keyword">void</span> *arg) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">char</span> *str;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Other thread about to call strerror().\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    str = strerror(EPERM);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Other thread: str (%p) = %s.\n&quot;</span>, str, str);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">char</span> *str;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pthread_t</span> tid;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    str = strerror(EPERM);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Main thread has called strerror().\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_create(&amp;tid, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, thread_func, <span class="literal">NULL</span>) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    assert(pthread_join(tid, <span class="literal">NULL</span>) == <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Main therad: str (%p) = %s.\n&quot;</span>, str, str);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
